<HEADLINE>
<P>
ANGELS SHOULD BE THE LAST TO COMPLAIN 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I think it is very rude of the Angels to refuse to play Seattle in the minor 
league park in Tacoma because they feel the facility is beneath the dignity of 
a major league team. After all, the Angel opponents have never objected to 
playing a minor league team in a major league park. 
</P>
<P>
 KEN MARCUS 
</P>
<P>
 Los Angeles 
