<P>
 Some of the top high school seniors in California will be featured, including 
Toby Bailey (UCLA), Tremaine Fowlkes (California), J.R. Henderson (UCLA), 
Kristaan Johnson (UCLA), Leif Nelson (Nebraska) and Ricky Price (Duke). 
</P>
<P>
 Simon, who will play at Arizona next season, led the Monarchs to the Southern 
Section I-A championship. 
</P>
<P>
 The Summer Pro League's rookies championship game will be played at 2:45 p.m. 
and the veteran's final will be at 7:30 p.m. 
</P>
