<P>
 "The Hancock family (Claiborne Farm) and Mrs. Perry have been staunch 
supporters of the Grayson-Jockey Club in the past," Edward L. Bowen, president 
of the Foundation, said in a statement. "We are extremely grateful that they 
would utilize the visibility of Lure for the benefit of research." 
